title: Millennial Money
overview: Millennial Money puts the "personal" in personal finance. Get an inside look at the lives and finances of millennials to see exactly how much they earn, what they spend it on and how they invest. From starting a business to changing careers, getting in and out of debt, creating an unusual income stream, or casting it all aside to start over again, young people reveal the steps they took to make it happen. Including how much they get paid, what they spend on food, shelter and fun, and how thy plan on saving for the future, Millennial Money takes a revealing look into the one area people seem to never talk about: their money.
